楚，以前没出现过这种现象。（综合 大象新闻 九派新闻）河南多地凌晨天空划过不明物体亮如白昼，居民：被震醒了"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ijfqt9uDV1t9xEAMaCDczOTQ1OTQ4INHBko0GMC04ughAA3IJNTAyNDkxMTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"731 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-995ec97ce6b5132551c775f7fcfff108_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1638259762.9835482","card_id":"Q_502341939","target":{"id":502341939,"title":"如何看待重庆一对新人邀请曾拆散他们的班主任证婚，班主任发言「被狠狠打脸」？对待早恋应该采取怎样的态度？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/502341939","type":"question","created":1638150266,"answer_count":233,"follower_count":884,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[982,6603,17205,39720,105508],"comment_count":39,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，重庆一段班主任在婚礼上，为学生当证婚人的视频逗乐网友。视频中的这对新人，曾在学生时代谈恋爱被班主任拆开，然而这对新人成功躲开了老师的「明枪」和家长的「暗箭」，十多年后还是走到了一起，在婚礼当天还请来当时的班主任当证婚人。曾拆散早恋学生的班主任 10多年后受邀当证婚人 班主任在台上发言像讲公开课一样，金句频出，并表示自己被这对新人的幸福狠狠打脸。 班主任为曾经被自己拆散的学生证婚？对于这个新闻，你怎么看？ 我们是否该重新认识早恋？对待早恋应该采取怎样的态度？ 你在学生时代有过早恋吗？班主任和家长用了哪些手段来「拆散」你们？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ijfqt9uDV1t9xEAMaCDczOTEyODg1IPrgkI0GMCc49AZABHIJNTAyMzQxOTM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"581 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b0a04da8139a4010403b7bf7dfc54a35_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1638259762.984271","card_id":"Q_498876754","target":{"id":498876754,"title":"朋友帮我开了一个蝴蝶刀，我的箱子我的钥匙，他要求卖了分一半给他，怎么办？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/498876754","type":"question","created":1636881349,"answer_count":169,"follower_count":261,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[156106,169142,566304],"comment_count":23,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_inf