第6个局点。王曼昱一个幸运的滚网球得分，15平。双方形成相持，孙颖莎失误，王曼昱第二次拿到赛点。关键时刻，孙颖莎接发球出界，17比15，王曼昱赢下第六局以4比2获胜夺冠，她坐在地上庆祝。连扳3局4-2战胜孙颖莎 王曼昱首夺世乒赛女单冠军"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ijfqt9uDV1t9xEAMaCDczOTY3NDM2ILL7lY0GMAI4zwFALHIJNTAyNTg4NDM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"38 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-833864563a067d70aff5febf501c0eb0_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"45_1638259763.0095508","card_id":"Q_501783252","target":{"id":501783252,"title":"孩子胆小，唯唯诺诺的，让我一度认为是不是自己的教育方式不行，大家有什么好的育儿经？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/501783252","type":"question","created":1637913342,"answer_count":125,"follower_count":238,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1395,2146,12046,24166,134321],"comment_count":7,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ijfqt9uDV1t9xEAMaCDczNzg4NzQ5IP6lgo0GMAc47gFALXIJNTAxNzgzMjUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0d5ae33e19fc140ccdc202318ade613_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1638259763.0099454","card_id":"Q_502207592","target":{"id":502207592,"title":"为什么有些老摄影师会推荐新手小白去买一些过时的机器？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/502207592","type":"question","created":1638081788,"answer_count":78,"follower_count":166,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[388,414,1097,3053,14760],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"美其名曰老机器性能足够，不会浪费钱。 但这不就是先入为主的认为摄影小白坚持不下去之类的吗？这合理吗…"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ijfqt9uDV1t9xEAMaCDczODgzMTE5IPzJjI0GMAM4pgFALnIJNTAyMjA3NTkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","t